      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains structurally flawless with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, ensuring the precision of the original M-variable differential lock. Every body panel retains its factory VIN tag, and the suspension geometry is dialed to OEM specifications. Mechanically impeccable, the VANOS system has been bulletproofed and the rod bearings serviced, offering a high-revving, visceral driving experience in its truest form.",
